:"typeIdentifier","text":"State","preciseIdentifier":"s:22ComposableArchitecture7ReducerP5StateQa"}]}]},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"name":"toValue","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A closure that returns a value from the given state."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"name":"reducer","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"A reducer builder closure to run when the value changes.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"oldValue"},{"type":"text","text":": The old value that failed the comparison check."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"code":"newValue","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":": The new value that failed the comparison check."}]}]}],"type":"unorderedList"}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"return-value","type":"heading","text":"Return Value","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A reducer that performs the logic when the state changes."}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Discussion"},{"name":"Important","type":"aside","style":"important","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"code":"onChange","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" operator is only capable of detecting changes made by the reducer","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"it is directly attached to. It does not observe changes that are made from other actions,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"such as parent actions.","type":"text"}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Use this operator to trigger additional logic when a value changes, like when a","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/BindingReducer","type":"reference"},{"text":" makes a deeper change to a struct held in ","type":"text"},